Package xyz.fsgek.common.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GekFile
    Interface to operate file, thread-safe.
    GekFileCache
    File cache service, provides cached IO methods.
    GekFileCache.CacheReadListener
    Listener for cache read.
    GekFileCache.CacheWriteListener
    Listener for cache write.
    GekFileCache.ChunkCache
    Cache interface used for GekFileCache, must support remove listener.
    GekFileCache.ChunkCacheGenerator
    Generator for file chunk cache.
    GekFileCache.ChunkCacheGenerator.RemoveListener
    Chunk cache remove listener.
    GekFileCache.FileAccessGenerator
    Generator for un-cached underlying file access.
    GekFileCache.FileReadListener
    Listener for underlying file read.
    GekFileCache.FileWriteListener
    Listener for underlying file write.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GekBuffer
    Utilities for Buffer, etc.
    GekFileCache.Builder
    Builder for GekFileCache.
    GekFileCache.Chunk
    Value for chunk cache, holds file chunk data and tail flag.
    GekFileCache.ChunkIndex
    Key for chunk cache, holds file path and index of cached chunk data.
    GekIO
    Input/Output utilities.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GekIOException
    Exception for IO.
